lead_paragraph: Nothing scares these Chicago Cubs. Not the stakes, the weight of history, a tough night at the plate or the prospect of going down two games to none in the franchise's first World Series in 71 years.

headline.print_headline: Rizzo, Zobrist Lead Cubs' Offensive Outburst in Game 2
